{"tid":280211,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"午後之紅茶諗一個童話故事","createTime":"2017-06-12T02:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T07:25:21.000Z","uid":118522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b0658d8a3b0b18f2ac610ad5963a09db141e75","tid":280211,"uid":118522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"午後之紅茶諗一個童話故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37ed1c65d8ff4c7366391a60df31d7795f5c144","tid":280211,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"一隻口渴的烏鴉找到了一個裝著午後之紅茶的瓶子。<br />\n<br />\n牠很高興的想喝裡面的午後之紅茶，但是午後之紅茶很少，烏鴉喝不到。<br />\n<br />\n於是，牠叼來許多小石子，投入瓶子裡。<br />\n<br />\n午後之紅茶漸漸升高，到了瓶口，烏鴉就喝到午後之紅茶了。"},{"pid":"3a06b875896b96cb0407c6f033a1f4cfefe021cc","tid":280211,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"功課自己做啦"},{"pid":"d3c3f1502bf258e5e50e08094cebc009813bade9","tid":280211,"uid":17368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:25:21.000Z","msg":"從前，有一位英國貴族，他喜歡在午餐後喝一杯紅茶。<br />\n最後，他死了。<br />\n<br />\n午後之紅茶"}]}